OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772758999
OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FThe US-Israeli war with Iran has
OL,7,Fentered its seventh day as the first
OL,8,FGovernment-chartered plane evacuating
OL,9,FBritish nationals from the region is
OL,10,Fdue to arrive in the UK.
OL,12,FThe flight took off from Muscat, the
OL,13,Fcapital of Oman, at 1.36pm GMT on
OL,14,FThursday.
OL,16,FThe Titan Airways flight is expected
OL,17,Fto arrive at London Standard shortly
OL,18,Fafter 1.15am on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
