OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772758999
OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FMore than 140,000 Britons have
OL,7,Fregistered their presence in the
OL,8,FMiddle East with the Foreign Office
OL,9,Fand 4,000 have returned home so far.
OL,11,FEtihad Airways announced late on
OL,12,FThursday that it would be resuming a
OL,13,F"limited commercial flight schedule"
OL,14,Fon Friday, including flights to
OL,15,FHeathrow.
OL,17,FThe US and Israel have continued to
OL,18,Fbatter Iran with nationwide strikes,
OL,19,Fand in turn, Iran has kept up
OL,20,Fretaliatory strikes on Israel, US
OL,21,Fbases and across the region.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
