OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772758999
OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister insisted that the
OL,7,Fspecial relationship is "in operation
OL,8,Fright now" and said on Thursday that
OL,9,Fan additional four British Typhoon
OL,10,Ffighter jets are being deployed to
OL,11,FQatar to strengthen "defensive
OL,12,Foperations" in the region.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer sought to highlight
OL,15,FUK-US intelligence-sharing on a "24/7
OL,16,Fbasis" amid the spiralling war.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@JO]sD@UOUtD@KO]wD@aOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772758999
OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FIt came as Mr Trump repeated his
OL,7,Fassertion that Britain's response has
OL,8,Fbeen "very disappointing" and that it
OL,9,Fshould be allowing America to use its
OL,10,Fbases "without question or hesitation".
OL,12,FSir Keir has tried to limit British
OL,13,Finvolvement in the conflict but
OL,14,Fdecided on Sunday that the joint UK-US
OL,15,FDiego Garcia site in the Chagos
OL,16,FIslands and RAF Fairford in
OL,17,FGloucestershire could be used by the
OL,18,FUS for "defensive" strikes to protect
OL,19,Fcountries being targeted by Tehran.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@YO]rD@GOUrD@fO]zD@HOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772758999
OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FHowever, the decision not to grant
OL,7,Fpermission for the first wave of
OL,8,Fmilitary action prompted anger from Mr
OL,9,FTrump, who said he was "not happy with
OL,10,Fthe UK" and, in a personal attack on
OL,11,Fthe Prime Minister, added: "This is
OL,12,Fnot Winston Churchill that we're
OL,13,Fdealing with."
OL,15,FThe two leaders last spoke during a
OL,16,Fcall on Saturday evening, Sir Keir
OL,17,Fconfirmed on Thursday.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@GO]sD@\OUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
