OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FIn an interview with American news
OL,7,Fwebsite Axios, Mr Trump said he should
OL,8,Fbe involved in choosing Iran's next
OL,9,Fsupreme leader.
OL,11,FHe dismissed possible successor
OL,12,FMojtaba Khamenei, son of the
OL,13,Fassassinated supreme leader Ali
OL,14,FKhamenei, as a "lightweight".
OL,16,FThe US president is reported to have
OL,17,Fsaid "I have to be involved in the
OL,18,Fappointment", comparing the situation
OL,19,Fto his removal of Nicolas Maduro in
OL,20,FVenezuela.
OL,26,@vD@POUvD@\O]yD@FOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
