OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FTrade union Prospect said a
OL,7,Frenegotiated Ministry of Defence
OL,8,Fcontract for some staff at Portsmouth
OL,9,FNaval Base, where HMS Dragon is being
OL,10,Freadied, may be contributing to delays
OL,11,Fto its deployment.
OL,13,FThe contract was based on the "fantasy
OL,14,Fthat conflict only occurs between nine
OL,15,Fand five", which means union members
OL,16,Fare volunteering to do overtime to get
OL,17,Fthe warship ready, the union said.
OL,26,@uD@_OUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
