OL,3,CIran war enters seventh day as first
OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,FAccording to reports, the war has
OL,7,Fkilled at least 1,230 people in Iran,
OL,8,Fmore than 100 in Lebanon, around a
OL,9,Fdozen in Israel and six US troops.
OL,11,FIn other developments on Thursday:
OL,13,F` Iran warned the US would "come to
OL,14,Fregret" sinking an Iranian warship in
OL,15,Fthe Indian Ocean on Wednesday.
OL,17,F` Azerbaijan accused Iran of attacking
OL,18,Fit with drones ` though Tehran denied
OL,19,Fthat.
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@GO]
