OL,4,CGovernment flight brings Britons home
OL,6,F` Israel issued a mass evacuation
OL,7,Fwarning for all Beirut's southern
OL,8,Fsuburbs as the fighting escalated with
OL,9,FLebanon's Iran-allied Hezbollah
OL,10,Fmilitants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
